1. *Zadovoljni* smo uspehom našeg tima. (We are *satisfied* with the success of our team.)
2. Oni su *zadovoljni* svojim novim autom. (They are *satisfied* with their new car.)
3. Moj šef je uvek *zadovoljan* mojim radom. (My boss is always *satisfied* with my work.)
4. *Zadovoljni* kupci su najbolja reklama. (Satisfied customers are the best advertisement.)
5. Kada je videla svoje rezultate, bila je *zadovoljna* svojim trudom. (When she saw her results, she was *satisfied* with her effort.)
6. *Zadovoljni* gosti su najbolji dokaz kvaliteta usluge. (Satisfied guests are the best proof of service quality.)
7. Nismo *zadovoljni* uslovima rada u ovom preduzeću. (We are not *satisfied* with the working conditions in this company.)
8. Klijenti su *zadovoljni* našim savetima i podrškom. (Clients are *satisfied* with our advice and support.)
9. Očekivali smo bolji rezultat, ali smo ipak *zadovoljni* postignutim. (We expected better results, but we are still *satisfied* with what we achieved.)
10. Njegova ljubav prema poslu čini ga uvek *zadovoljnim*. (His love for his job always makes him *satisfied*.)